{
  "text": "Ronksley et al. [CITATION_1] did so in a community cohort, in Canada. Using a community based population increases the generalisability of results as opposed to relying on, for example, a selected inpatient population. We did not identify any studies from the UK that compared hospital episode data to laboratory data.",
